text: Roos Oosterbaan (born 18 May 1979) is a Dutch wheelchair basketball player. She won a bronze medal at the 2012 Summer Paralympics, and 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played at the 2004 Summer Paralympics, 2008 Summer Paralympics, and 2014 Women's World Wheelchair Basketball Championship. == References == == Other websites == * INTERVIEW: Roos Oosterbaan (Netherlands) 2014 IWBF Women's World Wheelchair Basketball Champs, June 24, 2014 Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for the Netherlands Category:Dutch wheelchair basketball players
